{"tid":2489472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麵包師傅藏麵包棍六角匙 蘇文隆去年判囚9個月 潘敏琦今駁回上訴 需即時服刑","createTime":"2021-04-15T03:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T05:47:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0dcc517b2ec8f7c65298e76c07d4877744b32f","tid":2489472,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15042&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=f11fd48b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15042</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第廿八庭<br />\n#潘敏琦法官 #不服定罪及刑罰上訴<br />\n👤葉(30) #1112大埔 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有適合作非法用途的工具並有意圖用作非法用途使用<br />\n被告被控在2019年11月12日，在大埔安慈路燈柱附近的行人路，管有一支14吋的長木棍及1包六角匙，意圖將其用作非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n上訴人在2020年5月8日被落案起訴，並在同年8月10日不認罪受審，並在同月25日被蘇文隆主任裁判官裁定罪名成立並即時判處9個月即時監禁，上訴人即時提出保釋等侯上訴獲批。其上訴正式在2021年4月15日在原訟法庭法官潘敏琦席前處理。<br />\n<br />\n📌當時蘇文隆主任裁判官就本案的裁決和判刑理由：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8653&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=e944e204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8653</a><br />\n=====================<br />\n上訴方代表：#駱應淦資深大律師<br />\n=====================<br />\n🛑法庭即時駁回上訴人就本案的定罪及刑罰的上訴，上訴人需即時服刑🛑<br />\n<br />\n聆訊詳情後補。"},{"pid":"0497c4055f2b2e5ad1e4702af8859a187bec7d78","tid":2489472,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9485832916b1010ddce792596ed43dba7b21836f","tid":2489472,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0497c4055f2b2e5ad1e470